type":"markdown","source":"### 2.2 LightGBM Importance","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"lgbm = lgb.LGBMClassifier(random_state=42, verbose=-1)\nlgbm.fit(X, y)\n\nlgbm_importance = pd.DataFrame({\n    'Feature': feature_cols,\n    'Importance': lgbm.feature_importances_\n}).sort_values('Importance', ascending=False)\n\nplt.figure(figsize=(12, 8))\nsns.barplot(data=lgbm_importance, x='Importance', y='Feature', palette='magma')\nplt.title(\"LightGBM — Feature Importance\")\nplt.tight_layout()\nplt.show()\n\nprint(lgbm_importance.to_string())","metadata":{"trusted":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2026-03-31T11:28:56.377165Z","iopub.execute_input":"2026-03-31T11:28:56.377431Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-03-31T11:28:59.214724Z","shell.execute_reply.started":"2026-03-31T11:28:56.377406Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-03-31T11:28:59.213607Z"}},"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":"<Figure size 1200x800 with 1 Axes>","image/png":"\n"},"metadata":{}},{"name":"stdout","text":"                        Feature  Importance\n4              RIASEC_Realistic        3856\n5                 RIASEC_Social        3680\n3          RIASEC_Investigative        3508\n1           RIASEC_Conventional        2992\n2           RIASEC_Enterprising        2925\n0               RIASEC_Artistic        2230\n10        WS_Concern for Others        1753\n9        WS_Attention to Detail        1745\n8        WS_Analytical Thinking        1687\n16                 WS_Integrity        1614\n17                WS_Leadership        1591\n15                WS_Innovation        1440\n13              WS_Independence        1416\n27        WV_Working Conditions        1315\n20        WS_Social Orientation        1301\n21          WS_Stress Tolerance        1291\n19              WS_Self-Control        1287\n6         WS_Achievement/Effort        1214\n12             WS_Dependability        1213\n26                   WV_Support        1192\n11               WS_Cooperation  